{"_path":"/europe/england","_dir":"europe","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","_empty":false,"title":"英国","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"英国"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"英国"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"介绍"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"介绍"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"英国的主要城市有伦敦（London）、曼彻斯特（Manchester）、爱丁堡（Edinburgh）、贝尔法斯特（Belfast）、伯明翰（Birmingham）、布里斯托（Bristol）、剑桥（Cambridge）、卡迪夫（Cardiff）、格拉斯哥（Glasgow）、利兹（Leeds）、利物浦（Liverpool）、纽卡斯尔（Newcastle）、牛津（Oxford）和约克（York）等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"入境"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"入境"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"http://cs.mfa.gov.cn/zggmcg/ljmdd/oz_652287/yg_655203/rjjl_655213/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"入境"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"英国签证"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"英国签证"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"按英国法律规定，持中华人民共和国普通护照的人员入境或过境英国，均需事先办妥签证。申请人一般须就近向英国驻华使领馆在北京、武汉、沈阳、济南、重庆、成都、上海、杭州、南京、广州、深圳、福州、西安、昆明、长沙等地的外包签证中心申请。除特殊豁免和未满5周岁儿童外，一般须提供相应的指纹等生物信息。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"持中国香港和澳门特别行政区护照的人员，如系来英探亲旅游、从事商务等活动，且在英停留不超过180天的，无需办理签证。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"英国内政部自2008年起启用了移民计分制签证制度（PBS），将原本80多种工作、学习签证简化为五个层级的签证种类。如申请工作签证，一般需要提供英国境内雇主出具的担保人资质证明（COS），申请学生签证需要提供学校电子录取通知书（CAS）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"具体签证要求与手续，请事先向"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://visa.vfsglobal.com/chn/zh/gbr/attend-centre","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"英国驻华签证中心"}]},{"type":"text","value":"或"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/world/china","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"英国驻华使馆"}]},{"type":"text","value":"查询。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"一些趣味"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一些趣味"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"均来自"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"http://cs.mfa.gov.cn/zggmcg/ljmdd/oz_652287/yg_655203/jtcx_655231/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"领事服务网"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"除伦敦外，曼彻斯特、爱丁堡、格拉斯哥、利物浦、贝尔法斯特、伯明翰、纽卡斯尔等英国主要城市也有国际机场。希斯罗等主要机场航班进出港量趋于饱和，且英国多雨雪天气，延误事件时有发生。如遇天气、罢工等不可抗力导致的延误，请理性对待。如遇紧急情况可与中国驻英国使、领馆联系。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"介绍","depth":2,"text":"介绍"},{"id":"入境","depth":2,"text":"入境","children":[{"id":"英国签证","depth":3,"text":"英国签证"},{"id":"一些趣味","depth":3,"text":"一些趣味"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:europe:england.md","_source":"content","_file":"europe/england.md","_extension":"md"}